    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I also have both of Nigel Slater&#39;s Tender books, one of which I had delivered from the UK to Canada even though I am British and was going home to visit in a few weeks &#8211; I simply couldn&#39;t wait, although of course, you&#39;ve guessed it, I didn&#39;t get it until I got back to Canada! I haven&#39;t cooked anything from the fruit volume yet, I just admire the photos and the incredible writing. I&#39;ve made the chicken with sauteed celery from the vegetable version, but used young celery which resulted in chewing through string! The chicken was nice though.</p>
