    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>whipped it up before bed last night and had my first piece this morning. damn, gina, it is GOOD. didn&#39;t have golden syrup (as delightful and twee as it sounds), so i used more honey. also used salted butter (which i had on hand) and left out the salt. i will be bringing this one to every single event this fall and probably forever after. sometimes i get intimidated by the sheer size of nigel&#39;s books (aaron keeps them in the kitchen at the restaurant, not at home), so i probably never would have found this recipe on my own. THANK YOU!</p>
