    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#39;ve now made this twice with plums and twice with pears. We usually eat it with salted caramel ice cream from Strauss family creamery, which is divine. Today&#39;s version was my favorite: I only had Asian pears, so I poached them first in Marsala and sugar to make them a little richer. We boiled down the Marsala, and used it as a sauce for the cake. Delicious.</p>
