      <p>I love this cake and have made it a couple of times since you posted the recipe. I had some late season peaches that I needed to use up and substituted 3 peaches (cut into 8ths) for the plums, I also substituted 1/2 cup of barley flour for some of the regular flour. The results were excellent. Can&#39;t wait to make it again with plums now that they&#39;re all over the markets.</p>
